<!-- SYNERGY -->
<section class="synergy section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="synergy__inner">
      <div class="synergy__text">
        <span class="section-label">The Techo Philosophy</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">One Roof.<br/>Endless Capability.</h2>
        <p>The word "Techo" is derived from two powerful concepts: <strong>Techne</strong> — the ancient Greek art of professional craftsmanship — and a <strong>"Techo" (roof)</strong>, representing the shelter, stability, and protection we provide to our ecosystem.</p>
        <p>What makes Techo Traders unique is not just what each company does — it's how they work together. Techo Labs builds the tracking software that powers Techo Xpress. Techo Connect manufactures the hardware that strengthens both networks.</p>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn--primary" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Our Full Story</a>
      </div>
      <div class="synergy__visual">
        <div class="synergy__hub">
          <div class="synergy__hub-center">
